cetus.analysis
Class MayMod

java.lang.Object
  cetus.analysis.AnalysisPass
      cetus.analysis.IPAnalysis
          cetus.analysis.MayMod

public class MayMod
extends IPAnalysis

Class MayMod instantiates an IPA problem that computes may-modified variables. It is able to collect the subset of the solution by specifying "include" and "exclude" sets which are sets of type specifiers.
